Copy bin utils
--------------

./init/cpbin.sh

Committing
----------

You can commit with `commit` (ensure that its in /usr/bin).
This will read `git status` and commit with simple message from `gitmsg`.

Fonts
-----

./init/initfonts.sh

This will download and copy FantasqueSansMono to ~/.fonts.

Vim
---

./init/initvim.sh

Sets up Vim from scratch. Read script for details.

Symlinked config files
----------------------

./init/mksymlinks.sh

This script will create symlink for every file in linked/ directory in the
home directory. Old files are moved to ~/dotfiles.bak.

Suckless terminal
-----------------

cd st-0.8.1
git apply patches/*
sudo make clean install
